                    <partial name="Partials/_HomeSlider" />
                   
                    <p style="font-size:22px; font-family:Calibri" class="text-muted f-17 mt-3">
                        Would you like to have an easy HR system where you can even manage your company's permission, advance and expense items?
                    </p>
                    <p style="font-size:22px; font-family:Calibri" class="text-muted f-17 mt-3">

                        <a href="http://localhost:5254/Admin/Home/Login" style="color:darkred"> If you have already own HR package please click here and login </a>
                    </p>

                    <img src="images/home-border.png" height="15" class="mt-3" alt="">
